<p class="ayah 58-7" id="7" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Do not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْلَمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">knows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَكُونُ</span><span class="en second l