<p class="ayah 58-11" id="11" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلَّذِينَ ءَامَنُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O you who believe!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">When</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it is said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَفَسَّحُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Make room,`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَجَـٰلِسِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the assemblies</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱفْسَحُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then make room,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَفْسَحِ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah will make room</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for you.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">it is said</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱنشُزُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Rise up,`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱنشُزُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then rise up;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَرْفَعِ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah will raise</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">among you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوتُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">were given</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْعِلْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the knowledge,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دَرَجَـٰتٍ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) degrees.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْمَلُونَ</