<p class="ayah 58-14" id="14" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ أَلَمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Do not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you see</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[to]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَوَلَّوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">take as allies</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَوْمًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a people,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">غَضِبَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">wrath</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَيْهِم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) upon them?</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا هُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They (are) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of them,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَحْلِفُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they swear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْكَذِبِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the lie</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْلَمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">know.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>14<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 58-15" id="15" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَعَدَّ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah has prepared</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَدِيدًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">severe.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, [they]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">evil is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they used to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">do.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>15<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 58-16" id="16" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱتَّخَذُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">They have taken</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَيْمَـٰنَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their oaths</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جُنَّةً</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(as) a cover,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَصَدُّواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so they hinder</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) way of Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَلَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَذَابٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُّهِينٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">humiliating.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>16<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 58-17" id="17" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Never</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُغْنِىَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will avail</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنْهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْوَٲلُهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their wealth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْلَـٰدُهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their children</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">against</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَيْــًٔا‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(in) anything.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصْحَـٰبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) companions</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّارِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Fire,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِدُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will abide forever.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>17<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 58-18" id="18" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَوْمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(On the) Day</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَبْعَثُهُمُ ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah will raise them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَمِيعًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">all,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيَحْلِفُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then they will swear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Him</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">as</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَحْلِفُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they swear</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَكُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to you.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَحْسَبُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they think</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">شَىْءٍ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">something.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span cla